pos_examples: Now, saw board fire into medium part kumquat using saw teddy with awood socket, surface object_260, changing size from aboardsize kumquat_8 to aboardsize kumquat_8_78 through intermediate size aboardsize kumquat_8_78_96.
(do-saw-medium fire kumquat teddy socket object_260 kumquat_8 kumquat_8_78_96 kumquat_8_78)

Once you are done, please cut board fire into part kumquat using highspeed-saw bastion with awood socket, surface object_260, changing size from aboardsize kumquat_8 to aboardsize kumquat_8_78_96 through intermediate sizes aboardsize kumquat_8_78_96_97 and aboardsize kumquat_8_78_96_97_74.
(cut-board-large fire kumquat bastion socket object_260 kumquat_8 kumquat_8_78_96_97_74 kumquat_8_78_96_97 kumquat_8_78_96)

First, do immersion varnish on part kumquat using immersion-varnisher yew to change color to acolour screen with surface object_260 and then cut board fire into part kumquat using highspeed-saw bastion with awood socket, surface object_260, changing size from aboardsize kumquat_8 to aboardsize kumquat_8_44.

(do-immersion-varnish kumquat yew screen object_260)
(cut-board-small fire kumquat bastion socket object_260 kumquat_8 kumquat_8_44)

The next step is to do plane on part kumquat using planer object_50 to change surface from surface object_260 to smooth, color from acolour screen to natural, and treatment from treatmentstatus star_213 to untreated.
